nodes.text: Star Wars Weekly 102 is the one hundred second issue of the Marvel Star Wars UK series of comic books.
This issue reprints the third of four parts of the story printed in the US as Star Wars Annual 1.

The comic also includes the second part of a brand-new section called Star Profile featuring Carrie Fisher alongside a study-interview of his carrer until 1978 including the soon to-be-released Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back.
